This little tools helps to download a movie from the ARTE.TV mediathek.

currently the tool is restricted by
- downloads the german language movie
- tries to download only the HD version of the movie, if there isn't any it crashes


use it like this:

./arteDownloader.py -h
usage: arteDownloader.py [-h] [-v] ARTE_URL

positional arguments:
  ARTE_URL       ARTE URL

optional arguments:
  -h, --help     show this help message and exit
  -v, --verbose  increase output verbosity

  
